text: Bakayevo () is a rural locality (a selo) and the administrative center of Bakayevsky Selsoviet, Kushnarenkovsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 446 as of 2010. There are 8 streets. == Geography == It is located 25 km from Kushnarenkovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Kushnarenkovsky District
title: Bakayevo, Kushnarenkovsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
